verbose_text: Group 1 subjects showed a significant decrease in Resistin levels at T12 (p = 0.004) (Repeated Measures ANOVA : F-ratio = 3.17, p = 0.037), a significant increase in Adiponectin levels at T6 (p = 0.0018), and a non significant increase in Adiponectin levels at T12, as compared with T0 (XREF_TABLE, XREF_TABLE; XREF_FIG) (see XREF_TABLE).
